{"type":"message","id":"311933a6","parentId":"67755a61","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:44:00.856Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze what I found:\n\n1. **Gateway health**: The curl returned \"Not Found\" - this might mean the health endpoint isn't responding as expected, or the gateway is up but the endpoint is different. Let me try `openclaw gateway probe`.\n\n2. **Cron jobs**:\n   - `Nova-Moltbook-Engage`: OK (lastRunStatus: ok)\n   - `Nova-Background-Pulse`: ERROR - 6 consecutive errors, lastErrorReason: timeout - this is the job that's currently running\n   - `Sandbox-Pulse-10min`: ERROR - 1 consecutive error, timeout\n   - `workspace-self-improve`: OK\n   - `breakaway-rd`: ERROR - 1 consecutive error, timeout\n   - `Nova arxiv daily check`: OK\n   - `moltbook-test-cycle`: Never run (no lastRunAtMs)\n\nI'm noticing a pattern with the timeout errors across multiple jobs - `Nova-Background-Pulse` has been failing consistently with 6 consecutive errors, while `Sandbox-Pulse-10min` and `breakaway-rd` each have single timeout issues. The Moltbook and workspace jobs appear healthy, and the arxiv check completed successfully. I need to check if the timeout issue is systemic or specific to certain job types.\n\nThe background pulse job itself seems to be timing out during execution rather than being a configuration problem - the last error reason is timeout, not a missing file or bad env var. I should verify the gateway status and then check Moltbook notifications before deciding whether to log this as a persistent issue or attempt a fix.","thinkingSignature":"90255da6590e2ebd2caccf168a35bccdd10c0b8e4f9664735fc7b285c1c11a62"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_go71khtg2zjk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:18789/api/health 2>&1; echo \"EXIT:$?\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_go71khtg2zjk_2","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/notifications"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4538,"output":429,"cacheRead":11791,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16758,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774309426462}}
